plot: Nick's mother Kelly returns to help Adalind escape Europe with her baby. Meanwhile, Monroe and Rosalee prepare for their wedding.

Monroe dismisses Nick's objections to being his best man as dark sunglasses prevent Wes from noticing a Grimm's eyes when they vogue. Usurper prince Viktor executes and replaces his chief tracker for failing to kill Adalind, who escapes with the baby princess by airplane thanks to the Verrat resistance and Nick's mother, who directs them to Portland.—KGF Vissers
